els which trace stellar mass, halo mass, or star-formation rate.\nWe also find that strategies to follow up gravitational-wave events with\nelectromagnetic telescopes can be significantly optimized using the clustering\nproperties of their hosts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 4 Jan 2020 03:08:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-16"}
